com.inqwell.any.client.swing

Class ServiceInvocationEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • java.awt.AWTEvent
        • java.awt.event.InvocationEvent
          • com.inqwell.any.client.swing.ServiceInvocationEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActiveEvent, Serializable

    public class ServiceInvocationEvent
extends InvocationEvent
    Dispatch the execution of a Runnable and perform transaction cleanup afterwards. This event is placed on the awt event queue when an inq service is declared or requested to run on the swing thread.
